properties.name: cpnNotice
properties.value:
{"maxLevel": 1, "msg": "You open your eyes and cough. Saltwater burns your throat. You remember the storm, and the crash that left your ship in pieces.

You realize you need to find shelter. Use wasd or the arrow keys to move."}

properties.name: cpnNotice
properties.value:
{"maxLevel": 1, "msg": "You take a few steps, still weak from the ordeal. Through the glare of the sun, you see a creature to the north-east.

Press v to toggle nameplates."}

properties.name: cpnNotice
properties.value:
{"maxLevel": 1, "msg": "The seagull's eyes are bloodshot and in its beak you see a glinting locket. It stole your family heirloom!

Click on it to target it then press space to toggle auto-attack. Remember to stand close if you are using melee attacks."}
